{"tid":1979804,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"今日就分化下網上啲page同group先","createTime":"2020-04-19T16:22:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-22T18:39:14.000Z","uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1381dd44b9e82ef9840484ff93dd0c23de871c48","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:22:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />例如連登時事台、黑狗子女關注組咁，分化下又可以瓦解多個反抗平台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ab51ad1af6b765aaaf94f89cc75cbfc3ab9736a","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:27:15.000Z","msg":"黃店、黃page<br />\n<br />\n遲下就到黃民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無一個走得甩"},{"pid":"f675e417044574157ac5c9fdb99fa1eb872c52a1","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:34:25.000Z","msg":"見到不利自己嘅消息就丟淡佢<br />\n見到有利自己嘅消息行動就大煲特煲<br />\n再將對手一啲行為不斷誇張膠化，直到令人生厭<br />\n或者扮曬兩邊互屌嚟扯多啲人入局<br />\n開始成形嘅觀念就要騷擾、曲解，再內部破壞<br />\n開始變弱時就大搜捕，再上網落井下石辣慶班人，辣到佢哋互相懷疑，甚至懷疑自己<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n敵進我退，敵駐我擾，敵疲我打，敵退我追，網上一樣用得著嚟對付班香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd124426a95524b6344d8446f536465f7528e87","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:39:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b513fff45ce6c7d1aaf072b56f73470ac5fccf3e","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:40:18.000Z","msg":"最重要一樣，做五毛EQ真係要夠高，再加埋厚黑，根本冇得輸，有錢齊齊搵。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73e7d7507a85dedc47a43346e30f60230301d4f3","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:41:17.000Z","msg":"唔需要回覆啲人屌鳩自己嘅留言，你有你屌我有我講，適當時候爆一句又可以引到黃營鬼打鬼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ce2f311037a93fff906fe9c1e59b1ee96e91c62","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T16:43:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5d7d115a93a64eda589720a3ff79e959090dbd","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-19T19:09:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b527a801a0dd87363f9870e0a0e6bc03322962ac","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T05:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"633dea9d58a22bd420337825927baab1359c93f9","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:16:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71979418f661f7ffbc379d303d5b5779237b17a1","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T06:25:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da0dd5032831ddc90e6a3dd6b9a0e04f4e023e41","tid":1979804,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-22T18:39:14.000Z","msg":"推"}]}